      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just... i can't help but wonder if things would just be easier for everyone if i wasn't around. if i wasn't a constant problem to solve. it feels almost selfish to keep clinging on when i know it's just making their lives harder. wouldn't it be more peaceful for them if i just... let go?",
